body_html: I do get the same slow down on a single CPU. I ran Intel vtune profiler (for CPUs) on the same test image and it seems that its just not optimized. There needs to be better optimization for gemmlowp. Comparing it with the FP32 implementation that is optimized to a certain extent does better.
